## Generating Patches

```bash
# Stage test files ONLY
git add test/feature-name-test.ts test.sh

# Generate test patch
git diff --cached > test.patch

# Reset for clean state
git reset HEAD
git checkout .

# NO solution.patch - solvers create their own solutions
```

**Why No Solution Patch:**
- Solvers must understand the codebase themselves
- Multiple valid implementation approaches should work
- Tests define correctness, not a reference implementation
- Encourages diverse problem-solving strategies

